metadata.name: Bridge
metadata.description: You have been working on your current world for a long time and it’s time to move on.  The bridge between the two worlds that you have been straddling has been formed, but you still have a choice – maintain the status quo or choose to cross over.  If you continue to stay on the bridge, an old world will disappear behind you and new opportunities will materialize before you, but if you choose to cross over, all of those doors will open up before you. Will you let go, release yourself from your past and step into the unknown?
